<p>You are not yet participating in this challenge. What are yer? Chicken? <& /zaapt/common/icon.mhtml, name => 'emoticon_tongue' &></p>

<p>
     <a href="?act=accept">
         <& /zaapt/common/icon.mhtml, name => 'accept', title => "Accept" &>
         Accept this challenge!
     </a>
